                         Encoder/Ripper: SMiLE                         
                                                                        
   READNFO is just to say that this is fully in sync and that it is     
   not the best CAM ever devised. This needed a fair bit of filtering   
   that's why it's took us so long to encode. We tried to tone down     
   that rainbow tinge the best that we could but it still appears in    
   the daytime scenes pretty bad. Once we finished filtering the        
   video we dropped it in for converting, where we then ran our custom  
   encode settings over the file. Came out pretty sweet we must say.    
   This is watchable for typical CAM/TS downloaders, but if you are     
   fussy i'd give this one a miss. We can only hope that a new video    
   source pops up soon. As said above, audio has been sync checked      
   and it should be fully in sync throughout, the audio itself is       
   pretty hollow but is also pretty clear. First minute or so of the    
   video is a bit blurry and has a bit of a wobble, but apart from      
   that it's ok. Just remember that it's free and enjoy. 
